data.description: LOCATION, LOCATION, RENOVATION……….. This is a very rare opportunity to own a turn-key home in the charming central/downtown area of Pflugerville, Texas. The location alone is a value add with the walking and/or biking distance to the local restaurants, bars, HEB, shops, and parks.     This renovation was meticulously planned out and orchestrated with love and care. The folks at RAD Homes modified the original floor plan to open up the living area and kitchen to breath new life into the flow of the home. This home was stripped down to the bones, deep cleaned, and updated with the upmost care and modern flare.    When you walk into this home you will feel like you just stepped into a new build. Everything is fresh, clean, and new! The entire home and garage was professionally re-textured and sealed, making the home feel brand new.     The home features all brand new appliances in the kitchen as well as quartz countertops and new cabinets. The lighting was reconfigured with flush mount color spectrum adjustable LED’s.    Both bathrooms received full upgraded shower plumbing to Pex pipes, unibody low-profile elongated toilets, and High CFM exhaust fans with mood lights and built in Bluetooth Speaker capability. Custom made- to -fit vanities were installed to maximize the space of the bathrooms. New bath tubs and shower pans are outfitted with floor to ceiling tile.            The flooring throughout the home was replaced with a quality water resistant laminate with sound eliminating underlayment.    A newly constructed tall horizontal Zen Fence gives this home some great curb appeal and optimal privacy in the backyard.     In shorth, this home is in an amazing pocket neighborhood in central Pflugerville, and has had over 100k worth of upgrades put into it. The new owner of this home can feel confident that they will be able to live in this home for years without having to worry about costly maintenance or fixes, because we did the hard part for you.
